name: Bingo
description: Not just any ape… Bingo was born lucky. While others aped into rugs, Bingo aped into jackpots. Every token he touched turned into gold (or at least a solid 3x before lunch). They say Bingo once flipped a free mint into a Lambo, blindfolded, with gas fees at zero. His secret? Pure, unfiltered BASE-chain luck and a little meme magic. Now, the legend lives on through $BINGO, the meme coin of the lucky few. Backed by vibes, powered by apes, and running wild on Base. Because when the market gets bananas… you'll want Bingo on your side.
